Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.32,0:07:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.32,0:07:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The music stops, so it must be time to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,God is prompt, so we try to be prompt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.17,0:07:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 9 o'clock, God's here, so it's good to see you all again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.80,0:07:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Last week we were in Austin, so if you're from Austin and you're here today, say hello
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.61,0:07:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We start out, we have an interpreter here also.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.46,0:08:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear what she's saying, but she knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.76,0:08:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The rate my hearing is going, I'll be needing her soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.76,0:08:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm buttering her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.32,0:08:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I say what more than any other word in the language.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.78,0:08:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.28,0:08:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.86,0:08:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I have this African parrot that makes my what's even worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.34,0:08:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.18,0:08:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She said Merry Christmas this morning, so that's her message to the group.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.07,0:08:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been following the advance of her consciousness, you know, and she's learning all kinds of
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.09,0:08:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,language.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.72,0:08:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And now she says, ho, ho, ho, Merry Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.37,0:08:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When Jesus returns, she'd be all ready for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So, as you know, we always start out with the end of the lecture first and work back
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,to the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.59,0:09:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The realization, there's only a few things you really need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.40,0:09:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only a couple of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.72,0:09:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If you know just a few things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.69,0:09:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If you know the things very well, that's all you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.08,0:09:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,To merely hear them already begins the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.18,0:09:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Just before the world disappears altogether, you notice that everything is happening spontaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.33,0:09:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The most important thing to know is that everything is happening in and of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.58,0:10:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is being caused by anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.24,0:10:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All phenomena are the automatic consequence of the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.24,0:10:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The field is one of infinite, invisible, omnipotent power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.33,0:10:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All encompassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.23,0:10:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a giant electromagnetic field.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.23,0:10:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No beginning, no ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.12,0:10:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Either spatially or in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.15,0:10:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever and always present.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This field is infinitely powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.97,0:10:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The human mind cannot conceive of the infinite.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Except as a concept.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.36,0:10:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Its presence is exquisitely gentle and exquisitely powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.77,0:11:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The field is so powerful that potentiality is activated by the field to become an actuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.21,0:11:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All things happen by virtue of the infinite power of the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.24,0:11:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What the world considers evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the witnessing of creation which is continuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.41,0:11:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The unmanifest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.14,0:11:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The unmanifest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.14,0:11:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond the linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.56,0:11:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Becomes manifest by divine providence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,As the totality of creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.09,0:11:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And this happens effortlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.09,0:11:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Within the field then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.75,0:12:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Potentiality is actualized by intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.07,0:12:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.89,0:12:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Each thing comes forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Manifesting its karmic inheritance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You might say its karma is its innate potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.75,0:12:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And when conditions are appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.80,0:12:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the potentiality becomes an actuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.30,0:12:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,In and of itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.30,0:12:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,In and of itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.30,0:12:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,As a consequence of the infinite power of the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.30,0:12:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The field is so powerful that if you continuously hold the thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It will become a happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.60,0:12:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise no one will become enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.39,0:13:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.02,0:13:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,One's intention is all powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.89,0:13:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,See the ego is very clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And as the thing begins to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.89,0:13:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,As the potentiality begins to manifest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.89,0:13:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes credit for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.89,0:13:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Person goes and takes a pair of scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And cuts the stem into an apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And he thinks he made the apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.48,0:13:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And he thinks he made the apple drop to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.17,0:13:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how all things are happening like gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.49,0:13:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no.
