Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.22,0:26:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to the right school and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.26,0:26:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No, 207 then, there's quite a push.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.46,0:26:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a push for integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.46,0:26:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you see is unrest in society, contention, conflict, social discord, because the energies
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.54,0:26:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,below 200 now are in a world which calibrates at 207.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.89,0:27:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So pure rhetoric alone will not cut the ice anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.63,0:27:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got to be backed up by some facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.61,0:27:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.79,0:27:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A new paradigm then of social acceptance.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.79,0:27:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.79,0:27:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So social acceptance, integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.79,0:27:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I could have saved Martha, trip to jail, easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.79,0:27:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Martha, go to a 12 step meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.04,0:27:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,10th step is when we were wrong, we promptly admitted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.04,0:27:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All she had to do is say, well, look, if your stockbroker said he's thinking that something's
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.04,0:27:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,bottoming out, wouldn't you sell it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.04,0:27:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I would too.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.00,0:27:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'd fine her, you know, $50,000 and end the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.00,0:27:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.00,0:27:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So, but no, she's really in prison for lack of integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.04,0:27:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's the thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.04,0:27:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.04,0:27:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.54,0:27:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.54,0:27:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.54,0:27:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.54,0:27:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.54,0:27:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.54,0:27:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.54,0:27:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.54,0:27:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.54,0:27:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.47,0:27:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's really, she was convicted of lack of integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.31,0:27:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,When you lie to a federal jury, you know, that's why she's in jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.32,0:27:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Not for money.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.40,0:27:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Not for wealth.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.64,0:27:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Not for fame.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.77,0:28:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You see at 207, you go to prison for lack of integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.99,0:28:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.99,0:28:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a new paradigm.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.99,0:28:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, in the old days, you could have bought off everybody, and she wouldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.43,0:28:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, it's not so easy to buy everybody off.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.31,0:28:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see now a strange interface between the old culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.45,0:28:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.07,0:28:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,. .
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.57,0:28:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,at 190, and then interacting with the culture at 205 and 207, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.00,0:28:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's like you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.84,0:28:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so the advance of truth doesn't necessarily bring tranquil waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.64,0:28:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, it may disturb things for a period of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.52,0:28:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And people who have gotten involved in intense spiritual work,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.81,0:28:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,before they get there, they think it's going to be hearts and flowers
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.89,0:28:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and we're all going to sing hymns.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.25,0:28:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll dance around the maypole and have peace marches, peace vigils,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.01,0:28:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and that will bring about peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.03,0:29:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you find that it's quite the contrary, that you now have a new paradigm
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.09,0:29:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and reflected in this new paradigm is the downside of the old,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.25,0:29:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and so you have a conflict, a conflict going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.60,0:29:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have peace, all right, but it may take a few thousand years, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.28,0:29:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No point to being impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.88,0:29:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,To merely know that all things are happening in and of their own
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.60,0:29:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,with no external cause, because the difficulty in a group such as is here today
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.08,0:29:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,is a group like this is stuck in the Newtonian paradigm of reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.14,0:29:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The Newtonian paradigm is that there is a this causing a that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.84,0:29:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dualistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.80,0:29:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's also the very source of thinking that there is a separate individuality
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.01,0:30:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and a separate individual eye, a separate personal eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.15,0:30:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no separate personal eye talking here, going.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.39,0:30:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The field, the field, the presence, because of the audience,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.73,0:30:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,speaks back to itself as it speaks, and I don't have anything to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.53,0:30:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing to do with what is being said, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.58,0:30:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.87,0:30:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.23,0:30:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Many years ago, when the personal self, the infinite presence is so powerful
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.60,0:30:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,that it really extinguishes anything that is not itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.10,0:30:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And the personal self became disappeared and the mind became silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.65,0:30:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The side, the mind right now is still silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.88,0:31:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I listened to the mind, said nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.63,0:31:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither does yours, but you think it does, and that's the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.69,0:31:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we'll start out where to make that jump, you see, and then we'll go back to the lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.54,0:31:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind thinks there is a you, and this you is causing this sequence of events, sequential causality.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.67,0:31:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw through that in theology class.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.42,0:31:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to a Jesuit university.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.28,0:31:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The arguments for the presence of God is that there must be a great big capital A back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.52,0:31:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Which in itself is fallacious.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.52,0:31:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an idiotic thing, and at the time I was an atheist, and it's a stupid remark.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.94,0:32:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, a sequence arises from that which is not of the sequence, not of the sequence, not of the sequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.23,0:32:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the average person thinks there is a personal me, and it is causing these thoughts or actions in a chain reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.48,0:32:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Causality is.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.48,0:32:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This causing of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.48,0:32:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, there must be an entity causing all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.12,0:32:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a presumption.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.79,0:32:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind can't understand infinity, so it presumes that in the sequence of events there would be a prime cause of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.79,0:32:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,God must have a prime cause of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.79,0:32:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That which always has been obviously needs no cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.79,0:32:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.79,0:32:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where the thoughts are, and this is where there is a teaching, a mistranslation of the teaching of the Buddha.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.04,0:33:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That the infinite reality, enlightenment, is seeing between two thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.38,0:33:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,In the seeming nothingness and void.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.36,0:33:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, many of us spent years and years cross-legged, breathing in strange places, wearing sandals, incense, the whole.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.96,0:33:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking for the space between A, B, and C.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.03,0:33:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Did anybody here ever find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.03,0:33:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.65,0:33:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe somebody says yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.65,0:33:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you're a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.65,0:33:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it cannot be found between the thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.65,0:33:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a mistranslation of the Buddha.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.65,0:33:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But, endless lifetimes have been spent.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.80,0:33:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nico and I are experts at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.80,0:33:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We spent lifetimes as Hinayana monks.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.12,0:33:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Pathway of negation, not this, not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.12,0:33:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, between.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.89,0:33:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot catch the infinite space between thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.18,0:34:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the mind is what's looking for the space between two thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.04,0:34:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And the mind cannot catch something that happens in less than one ten-thousandth of a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.17,0:34:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind is limited to one ten-thousandth of a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.62,0:34:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the mind is unable.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.62,0:34:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's today's lecture's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.62,0:34:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Observing and witnessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.68,0:34:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind, as we will see later, can't move fast enough to catch it between two thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.68,0:34:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got to be faster than one ten-thousandth of a second to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.68,0:34:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And it can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.77,0:34:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind cannot move faster than one ten-thousandth of a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.80,0:34:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, when a rabbit runs across the road, you put the brake on.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.32,0:34:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're quick and honest, you'll see that it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.97,0:34:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, the personal self congratulates itself that I stepped on the brake.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.48,0:35:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, it already braked.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.48,0:35:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the I, in one ten-thousandth of a second, claims authorship.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.48,0:35:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the difference between enlightenment and non-enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.93,0:35:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in that one ten-thousandth of a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.38,0:35:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I had the good fortune when I was very young that I caught the ego doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.57,0:35:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I caught it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.40,0:35:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It had already saved the rabbit's life and braked.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.40,0:35:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I caught the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.40,0:35:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I caught it claiming credit.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.40,0:35:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But I knew it had already happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.40,0:35:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,At the moment it said, I, the phenomena had already occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.17,0:35:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that was fortuitous.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.49,0:35:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,At that young age, I didn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.49,0:35:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't understand the implication of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.74,0:35:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.74,0:35:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if you cannot find the infinite reality between the thoughts,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.74,0:35:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,then where is the infinite reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.90,0:35:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And here is where it is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.32,0:36:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Beneath all the thinkingness is silence, void, silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.17,0:36:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The source of thinkingness, then, is an infinite silence and infinite peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.17,0:36:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you go in there, it's hard to lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.17,0:36:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'm not going to go in there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.06,0:36:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you feel weak and you begin to weep and you want to leave the world as soon as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.06,0:36:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.06,0:36:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So, anyway, it's the infinite silent field out of which your consciousness and your thinkingness is arising.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.54,0:36:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So, your thoughts are not arising this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.54,0:36:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Each one is being individually created sequentially.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.54,0:36:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,See there?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.54,0:36:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.83,0:36:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Each one is being independently sequentially.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.83,0:37:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So, instead of like billiard balls, thoughts are really like flying fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.28,0:37:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember World War II, we were in something or other sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.83,0:37:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't remember what sea it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.83,0:37:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, flying fish are flying out and landing on the deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.86,0:37:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So, a flying fish arises here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.86,0:37:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,All of a sudden, over here, another flying fish comes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.86,0:37:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here, another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.86,0:37:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Another one comes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.86,0:37:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Each one is coming up separately individually.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.86,0:37:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Of its own nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.17,0:37:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Spontaneously emerging of its own nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.17,0:37:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Because its nature, as a flying fish, is to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.42,0:37:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody is forcing it to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.42,0:37:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody is causing it to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.45,0:37:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The nature of the flying fish is it gets a kick out of doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.45,0:37:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you'll see how sick and weird the human mind is.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.61,0:38:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This fish comes up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.80,0:38:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This fish comes up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.80,0:38:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This fish comes up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.80,0:38:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And some idiot who's always a professor at some university.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.84,0:38:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They're always a professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.28,0:38:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Will tell you that the fish are triangulating.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.41,0:38:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's always this incredible mathematics.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.32,0:38:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You got to go through all the formulas and crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.39,0:38:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Demonstrates the triangulation of fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.96,0:38:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what your mind does.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.96,0:38:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So, your mind is the idiot scientist.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.96,0:38:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The idiot professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.99,0:38:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So, standing in your way is not ignorance.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.02,0:38:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.02,0:38:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the idiot professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.63,0:38:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The fish doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.17,0:38:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The fish just is what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.72,0:39:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.97,0:39:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Each one of us just is what we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.97,0:39:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not caused by anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.52,0:39:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no cause for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.52,0:39:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Creation is the unfolding of the unmanifest becoming manifest.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.45,0:39:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The infinite potentiality becoming manifest.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.45,0:39:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is by virtue of the incredible power of the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.80,0:39:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That explains and now we understand how karma works.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.99,0:39:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, each one of us are karmic inheritance.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.62,0:39:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is sort of like a software program.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.62,0:39:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all born with a software program.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.62,0:39:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The brain is your hardware.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.78,0:39:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's genetically engineered.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.78,0:39:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got nothing to do with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.61,0:39:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're born with consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.61,0:39:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you're born with this software programming.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.61,0:39:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Software.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.61,0:40:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your karmic inheritance.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.09,0:40:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That defines who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.28,0:40:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Your calibrated level.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.28,0:40:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody has a calibrated level of consciousness at the moment they're born.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.28,0:40:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment you're born, you already have a calibratable level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.28,0:40:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Without karma, how would you explain such a phenomena?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.38,0:40:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This now plays.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.38,0:40:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the hardware of the brain plays any software you put on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.38,0:40:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the karma is your software.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.38,0:40:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The karmic inheritance.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.38,0:40:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,All the decisions made through great eons of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.56,0:40:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, because of the software, you might say you're like an iron filing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.11,0:40:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Every spiritual decision then tends to change the configuration.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.36,0:40:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say you've got a little karmic body.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.36,0:40:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like caramel taffy or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.36,0:41:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All the decisions you've made have positioned it to be the way it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.36,0:41:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, in an infinite power, in an infinite field, like an electromagnetic field,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.23,0:41:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,this little iron filing is positioned as a consequence of the power of the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.03,0:41:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The field is so infinitely powerful that as a little iron filing,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.12,0:41:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you automatically go to where you fit in the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.44,0:41:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,As a consequence of that which you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.27,0:41:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,in the power of the field determines all phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.27,0:41:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,When and where you're born, how long you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.00,0:41:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And we discovered also through karmic research, through kinesiologic research,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.44,0:41:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you have a calibrated level of consciousness at birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.44,0:41:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,People who are born are calibrated at 40.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.48,0:42:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,60, 80, 200, 300, 400.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.94,0:42:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, at the moment of birth, the time of death is already preset.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.90,0:42:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that fatalism?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.90,0:42:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.90,0:42:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You can call it whatever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.90,0:42:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact is you enter already with a certain level of potential,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.90,0:42:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.12,0:42:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And your exit is already prearranged.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.92,0:42:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't have to worry about dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.92,0:42:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all handled.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.48,0:42:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the scary thing about this world is not...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.54,0:42:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The scary thing is how do you get out of here?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.54,0:42:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They keep closing all the doors, curing all these illnesses, safety features.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.54,0:42:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you can't get out of this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.54,0:42:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We're trapped. How are you going to get out of this place, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.54,0:42:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting here is easy. Getting out of here, how are you going to get out?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.67,0:42:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.37,0:43:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to get an exit permit from the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.79,0:43:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's not predestination, which is something else altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.35,0:43:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.35,0:43:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,your time is limited and the time of leaving is already preset.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.35,0:43:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sort of like getting a...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.60,0:43:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you call a computer disc now with a movie on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.60,0:43:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,DVD? What do you call them?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.73,0:43:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,DVD, yes. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.73,0:43:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,When you buy a DVD, the end of the sturdy is already in the tape
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.73,0:43:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,or the disc, what do you call it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.73,0:43:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The end of the sturdy is already there.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.24,0:43:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that it hasn't unrolled yet doesn't mean it's not there.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.24,0:43:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's like you're born with this computer disc CDD thing in your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.24,0:43:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This karmic CDB? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.56,0:43:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,DVD.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.11,0:43:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? DVD. DVD.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.11,0:44:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're born with a karmic DVD.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.57,0:44:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,However, you can play it on your computer and you can change the story as it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.80,0:44:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But when the end of the disc arrives, that's the end of the disc, folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.80,0:44:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you listen to what we say in the lectures,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.94,0:44:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,you will be very, very happy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.94,0:44:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go now, you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.44,0:44:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.44,0:44:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.34,0:44:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I had a huge psychiatric practice for many years
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.50,0:44:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and even after retirement, they didn't have anybody to go to the nursing homes
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.50,0:44:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and various places.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.50,0:44:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So in the county, I used to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.50,0:44:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,30,000 miles a year, running around doing nursing homes and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.50,0:45:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Every nursing home always has an old crone strapped in a wheelchair.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.08,0:45:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,She's got all these tubes, pipes hanging down there,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.36,0:45:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,all these devices, machines, computerized stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.88,0:45:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and she's always going,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.88,0:45:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Help! Help! Help! Help! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.94,0:45:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They say, Doctor, Doctor, can't you do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.94,0:45:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She keeps, Help! Help! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.94,0:45:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Help! Help! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.35,0:45:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what she wants, but it's illegal.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.35,0:45:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.88,0:45:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.40,0:45:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't let me out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.40,0:45:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot leave this world without Medicare permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.52,0:45:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Medicare breaks. It's not permissible.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.68,0:46:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull all these tubes and things out.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.68,0:46:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.68,0:46:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She keeps trying to pull the tube out, you know, because she wants to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.68,0:46:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do they do? They strap her arm down. Literally.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.07,0:46:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Tie down their arm so you can't croak.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.07,0:46:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And get the hell out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.16,0:46:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Before things get worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.62,0:46:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so you come in with this karmic program,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.02,0:46:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, your software.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.02,0:46:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got already a calibratable level of consciousness at the moment of birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.60,0:46:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The level of consciousness will determine what kinds of choices and options
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.60,0:46:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,you will have to make decisions about.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.69,0:46:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, everyone is born under the most karmically optimal conditions
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.42,0:46:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,for their evolution and growth.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.42,0:46:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a major discovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.42,0:47:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see if that's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.42,0:47:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody knows Susan, but I want to make sure everybody knows Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.96,0:47:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Without whom, we wouldn't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.96,0:47:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so the moment of...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.18,0:47:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What did we ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.53,0:47:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment of death is only a percent?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.53,0:47:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. No, it was karmic potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.63,0:47:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes. Everyone's...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.63,0:47:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The circumstances of your birth
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.63,0:47:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,are perfectly aligned with your karmic potential
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.63,0:47:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,to potentiate your evolution and growth.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.63,0:47:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to ask, that will learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.63,0:47:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And the answer to that is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.63,0:47:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist. True.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.33,0:47:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That gets rid of self-pity, folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.43,0:47:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.43,0:48:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The competition for being a victim in the poor me
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.84,0:48:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,is so severe in society.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.84,0:48:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, if you get to be more awful and pathetic than somebody else,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.84,0:48:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,they just...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.84,0:48:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They're so full of envy and hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.84,0:48:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They just hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.00,0:48:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My condition is worse than your condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.69,0:48:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Being the martyr, the victim of injustice,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.69,0:48:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,is the keynote to American society today.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.79,0:48:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.79,0:48:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So realizing that whatever the circumstances of your birth were,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.79,0:48:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,hardship, illnesses, death of parents,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.01,0:48:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,sexual predation, anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.01,0:48:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,is part of one's karmic inheritance.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.10,0:48:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Karma has its upside.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.90,0:48:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It also has the necessity for the undoing
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.90,0:48:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,of things, the undoing of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.93,0:48:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So if we accept the less pleasant things about our life
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.93,0:49:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and get that it's an undoing, an undoing,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.12,0:49:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore to be grateful for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.37,0:49:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,somehow, when you reach a certain level of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.40,0:49:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,then you remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.40,0:49:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You remember what the events were in previous life,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.40,0:49:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,in a prior life, what the world would call a prior life.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.40,0:49:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all one life, but prior incarnation.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.56,0:49:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is infinite in dimension can only have a beginning and an ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.56,0:49:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So your consciousness has always been.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.56,0:49:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The field out of which your consciousness arises
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.40,0:49:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,has always been.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.56,0:49:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And because it has always been,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.14,0:49:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,it will always be.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.27,0:49:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Death is not a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.14,0:49:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.14,0:50:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the people that dashes your final hopes, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.14,0:50:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you have to accept responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.14,0:50:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Death is just, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.14,0:50:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,it's long for a cop-out, a cop-out.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.14,0:50:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you can't cop-out with physical death.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.14,0:50:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you didn't undo it all,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.14,0:50:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,you come back again until you undo it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.14,0:50:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So, therefore, the vicissitudes of life
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.33,0:50:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,we can look at from wisdom and say,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.62,0:50:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what it's serving right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.62,0:50:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,but obviously it is serving something,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.62,0:50:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,either individually or collectively,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.62,0:50:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,because people also have collective karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.62,0:50:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? Collective karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.62,0:50:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,10,000 people kill 50,000 innocent civilians.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.00,0:50:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, how do you undo that?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.90,0:50:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How do the Vikings undo butchering
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.90,0:50:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,tens of thousands of innocent civilians?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.90,0:50:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Little babies in their crib.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.90,0:51:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you undo that?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.32,0:51:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to get to heaven,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.32,0:51:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you're going to have to undo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.32,0:51:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you need an opportunity to undo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.32,0:51:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So, karma prepares the infinite possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.73,0:51:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, we all inherit now,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.73,0:51:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,by virtue of this life,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.73,0:51:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore, is a gift,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.73,0:51:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,because through this life,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.73,0:51:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,we can undo that which was negative and a deterrent,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.76,0:51:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and we can align ourself with that which is integrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.04,0:51:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The only difficulty is that the world has never known
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.04,0:51:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,truth and falsehood and what is integrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.04,0:51:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's difficult, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.04,0:51:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to live a life without a compass.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.04,0:51:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You only have the say-so of tradition and religion.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.04,0:51:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, traditional religion told you which way is truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.04,0:51:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we need the...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.08,0:51:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to call it? Number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.08,0:51:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Number one or number uno.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.08,0:51:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you call that thing? Slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.04,0:51:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.71,0:52:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Slide. Ta-dum!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.71,0:52:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They've become relatively well-known.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.22,0:52:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The map of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.22,0:52:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the levels of man throughout all of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.22,0:52:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,as recorded throughout all of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.25,0:52:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Different wording and different cultures,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.25,0:52:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,but they always boil down to exactly the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.25,0:52:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.25,0:52:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And we call these the levels of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.57,0:52:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You can calibrate their relative energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.57,0:52:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.02,0:52:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.02,0:52:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,In doing this, the numbers became so large,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.28,0:52:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to switch to logarithmic.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.28,0:52:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Logarithmic.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.92,0:52:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, each of these numbers are 10 to that power.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.16,0:52:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is 10 times 10 times 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.16,0:52:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,250 times.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.16,0:52:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,10 times 10 times 10 times 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.16,0:52:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You do that 250 times.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.16,0:52:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You see that's a pretty big number.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.16,0:53:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it wouldn't fit on the blackboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.16,0:53:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we went to logarithmic.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.20,0:53:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We discovered that anything that ever existed, now or ever,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.20,0:53:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,it can be calibrated on a scale of one to a thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.28,0:53:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We said, what's the highest consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.28,0:53:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that's ever walked this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.28,0:53:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And we got the great avatars.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.28,0:53:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus Christ, Buddha, Krishna, Zoroaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.08,0:53:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the infinite...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.08,0:53:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the top potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.30,0:53:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The reasons for it are not important.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.30,0:53:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But, frankly, it's because of the nature
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.30,0:53:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,of protoplasm and the central nervous system
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.30,0:53:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,can only handle up to a power.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.30,0:53:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,See, because you're talking logarithmically now,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.30,0:53:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,as frequencies, energies go up,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.30,0:53:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the frequency gets higher and higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.30,0:53:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The human nervous system, frankly,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.30,0:53:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,has great difficulty handling anything
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.30,0:53:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,over maybe 750.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.30,0:54:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,From 750 up, you really should be in a different dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.54,0:54:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,From one to a thousand, we discovered then
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.54,0:54:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that we could calibrate the consciousness level
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.54,0:54:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,of anything on earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.54,0:54:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything, now or ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.54,0:54:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And we discovered, as I said, the kinesiologic test.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.54,0:54:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,When I saw Diamond do it, I realized it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.80,0:54:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness is like a giant electrostatic field.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.80,0:54:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember on the electrostatic speakers?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.80,0:54:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a membrane, electrostatically charged membrane.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.80,0:54:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, when you bring a charge up to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.80,0:54:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it reacts with an equal and opposite reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.80,0:54:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If you bring up...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.05,0:54:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Those of you who know physics will laugh at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.44,0:54:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say we bring up 32 frequencies.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.44,0:54:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Three protons and 32 neutrons,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.44,0:54:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,or what do you call them?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.44,0:54:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Negatrons.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.44,0:54:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Electrons.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.78,0:54:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And protons.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.78,0:54:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.61,0:54:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever the field holds,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.61,0:54:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,an equal and opposite reaction shows up.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.61,0:55:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in the presence of truth then,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.50,0:55:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness recognizes...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.50,0:55:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The difference between truth and falsehood,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.50,0:55:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and it recognizes the electrostatic charge,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.50,0:55:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you might say.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.50,0:55:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The higher truth goes up,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.50,0:55:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the higher and more powerful its charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.50,0:55:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So, when we calibrate something,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.85,0:55:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I hold it silently in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.85,0:55:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,People say, you're suggesting...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.92,0:55:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget, kinesiology has been examined,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.92,0:55:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, for decades by thousands of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.92,0:55:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, every argument you can think of
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.92,0:55:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,has already been looked at by thousands of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.92,0:55:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't influence what she's thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.30,0:55:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,because I don't tell her what I'm thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.30,0:55:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We only verbalize it when we have an audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.49,0:55:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If I want to know something,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.56,0:55:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to spend the time and energy
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.56,0:55:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,talking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.56,0:55:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Once in a while she'll say, what was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.56,0:55:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.88,0:55:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.45,0:56:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one I haven't had a chance to ask yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.25,0:56:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I have permission to ask that.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.25,0:56:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.25,0:56:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm thinking calibrates over 200 resistances.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.25,0:56:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,300.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.66,0:56:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,250.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.08,0:56:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,260.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.30,0:56:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm holding in mind is a phenomenon.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.30,0:56:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,250.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.30,0:56:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,260.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.30,0:56:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Telepathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.30,0:56:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We never did calibrate telepathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.30,0:56:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It says 250.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.00,0:56:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So, obviously, she didn't know what I was thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.00,0:56:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,because I've had it on my disk for a couple of months.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.00,0:56:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday I'll ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.00,0:56:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Telepathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.00,0:56:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We never did ask it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.41,0:56:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of people have experienced it on various levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.48,0:56:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,People who go for silent weekends
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.48,0:56:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,very often
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.48,0:56:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,become very adept at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.48,0:56:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I went on a...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.86,0:56:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it was only a four or five day silent retreat,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.86,0:56:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and within 24 hours
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.92,0:56:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody was telepathic.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.92,0:56:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't even think butter.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.92,0:56:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You would sit down
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.92,0:57:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and somebody would just hand you butter
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.92,0:57:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,like they knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.63,0:57:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of our staff have recently been
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.63,0:57:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,on silent weekends
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.63,0:57:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and they say it's sort of magical and mystical.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.63,0:57:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So you discover that telepathic capacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.63,0:57:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that you're consciously thinking a thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.63,0:57:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,but what you're holding in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.63,0:57:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,even non-verbally
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.63,0:57:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,is somehow knowable by other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.63,0:57:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, 250, that's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.63,0:57:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the way we do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.63,0:57:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to influence her in any way.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.63,0:57:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so sophisticated
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.88,0:57:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and skilled at this over the years
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.88,0:57:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that it doesn't influence her.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.88,0:57:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But just to make sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.88,0:57:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea what was going to come up
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.88,0:57:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,about telepathy myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.88,0:57:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So we discovered
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.10,0:57:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,you can calibrate everything
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.10,0:57:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,on a scale of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.10,0:57:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,that goes from one to a thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.10,0:57:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The critical level,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.20,0:57:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and I forgot my pointer today,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.20,0:57:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I always take it where I don't need it
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.20,0:57:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and forget it where I need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.20,0:57:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We found that
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.96,0:57:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,everything that is true
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.96,0:58:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates 200 and up,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.96,0:58:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.83,0:58:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So then we,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.83,0:58:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,because having been a psychiatrist,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.83,0:58:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,psychoanalyst, etc.,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.83,0:58:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,we naturally calibrated these things
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.83,0:58:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,according to the
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.86,0:58:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,classical levels
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.86,0:58:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,of human consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.04,0:58:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Each level then
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.04,0:58:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,has its own way of
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.13,0:58:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,understanding or perceiving God,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.52,0:58:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,including atheists.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.52,0:58:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Atheists can be predicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.87,0:58:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Their view of themself,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.18,0:58:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,a person's opinion of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.56,0:58:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We give this level
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.27,0:58:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,a name
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.27,0:58:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,that's common and familiar
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.27,0:58:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,so everybody knows
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.27,0:58:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,what grief is,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.27,0:58:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody knows what shame is.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.81,0:58:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we have the emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.81,0:58:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,that goes with it, emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.81,0:58:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you see
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.81,0:58:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,every day's headlines.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.81,0:59:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Every night's news broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.81,0:59:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You can calibrate
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.81,0:59:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,everything that happens on the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.81,0:59:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is the process
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.81,0:59:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,going on in consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.81,0:59:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,on the far right.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.93,0:59:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This plus knowing how to do kinesiology
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.93,0:59:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,can give you an answer
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.93,0:59:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,to anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.49,0:59:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.05,0:59:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,mankind in a way has
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.60,0:59:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the most incredible gift
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.60,0:59:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,it's ever received.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.60,0:59:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, the revelation
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.60,0:59:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,of the great teachers in history.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.62,0:59:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The gift of how to tell truth from falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.62,0:59:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This world,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.29,0:59:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and this is hard to get,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.45,0:59:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,does not know truth from falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.45,0:59:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This world does not know
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.35,0:59:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,truth from falsehood,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.35,0:59:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,nor does it have any test or capacity
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.35,0:59:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to differentiate the two.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.92,0:59:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Convincingness has nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.75,1:00:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The most convincing, persuasive
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.75,1:00:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,politicians in history
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.03,1:00:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,have led mankind
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.09,1:00:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,to death by the tens of millions
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.09,1:00:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,in my lifetime,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.09,1:00:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,tens of millions
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.09,1:00:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,died as a result of the
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.67,1:00:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,rhetorical,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.67,1:00:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,oratorical excellence of Adolf Hitler,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.67,1:00:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Stalin,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.08,1:00:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Milosevic,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.50,1:00:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the fallacy of Marxism,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.67,1:00:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,etc.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.99,1:00:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The human mind
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.24,1:00:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,so, by the tens of millions
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.24,1:00:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,people salute
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.24,1:00:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and worship falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.24,1:00:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Salute and worship
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.44,1:00:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,leaders who calibrate at 50.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.44,1:00:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up their lives
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.01,1:00:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,for leaders who calibrate at 50
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.01,1:00:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,worse than
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.01,1:00:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Machine Gun Kelly.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.30,1:00:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Worse than Machine Gun Kelly.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.61,1:01:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Lower than Machine Gun Kelly.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.61,1:01:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,People give up their lives
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.61,1:01:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,for them.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.61,1:01:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Donate all their properties.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.61,1:01:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sacrifice their children.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.61,1:01:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Send their sons off to war.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.61,1:01:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,To fight for illusion.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.16,1:01:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So really this is
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.53,1:01:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,one of the greatest gifts mankind
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.53,1:01:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,has ever really received.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.53,1:01:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only dawned on me more and more recently.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.53,1:01:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What an incredible
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.98,1:01:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,it's probably the most
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.98,1:01:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,valuable
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.98,1:01:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,gift we own right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.01,1:01:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Just think what you could do
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.23,1:01:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,if you could know truth from
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.23,1:01:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,falsehood about anything,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.23,1:01:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,anytime.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.32,1:01:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How would it make your life different?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.96,1:01:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The only requirement
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.31,1:01:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,to get an honest answer
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.31,1:01:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,is that you have to
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.31,1:01:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,yourself be aligned
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.50,1:01:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and committed to integrity
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.50,1:01:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and truth. That eliminates
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.53,1:02:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,85%
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.52,1:02:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,of the world's population.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.52,1:02:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, what we're talking about
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.04,1:02:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,today is accessible
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.04,1:02:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to only 15% of the world's
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.04,1:02:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,population. It calibrates
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.04,1:02:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,over 200. If the purpose
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.15,1:02:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,of asking the question is personal
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.15,1:02:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,selfishness, then the answer
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.15,1:02:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,is unreliable.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.47,1:02:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,When you ask for something, people say
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.47,1:02:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,can I use kinesiology about my
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.47,1:02:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,business? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.47,1:02:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So long as you ask only in the name of
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.47,1:02:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,the highest good. Anything
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.47,1:02:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,in reference to your personal life.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.47,1:02:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You can say it is in
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.47,1:02:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,the highest good. The highest good
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.47,1:02:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,meaning for the world,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.47,1:02:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,for society, for your employees,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.47,1:02:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,for your employees and their families.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.47,1:02:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,For the good and welfare
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.47,1:02:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,after all, everyone
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.53,1:02:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,who has any kind of money is now
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.53,1:02:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the steward of that money.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.53,1:02:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So you now have like a moral responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.53,1:02:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The minute you have money, you have in a way
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.53,1:02:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,a certain moral responsibility
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.53,1:02:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,to be a responsible steward for that money.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.53,1:03:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The taxpayers have worked
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.53,1:03:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,hard for that money.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.60,1:03:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We expect our public
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.60,1:03:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,officials to
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.63,1:03:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,be considerate of that. We've all
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.63,1:03:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,busted our chops for that
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.40,1:03:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,money.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.59,1:03:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So if
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.59,1:03:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the intention of the question is
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.59,1:03:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,integrous and you yourself calibrate over
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.59,1:03:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,200, then the reliability
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.59,1:03:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,should be excellent and it's like riding
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.59,1:03:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,a bicycle, you just need a little experience
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.59,1:03:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,with it. So you can say
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.20,1:03:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,it's in the name of the highest
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.20,1:03:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,good that my company
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.20,1:03:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,by this other little corporation
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.20,1:03:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,that we expand,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.29,1:03:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,we triple the size of our restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.29,1:03:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The way to go broke in the restaurant
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.68,1:03:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,world is to be very successful and then
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.68,1:03:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,double it, double the size of the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.68,1:03:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever seen
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.68,1:03:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,a little thriving Chinese restaurant,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.68,1:03:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, there's steam all over,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.68,1:03:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Italian restaurant, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.68,1:03:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you can see the chef there with the spaghetti
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.68,1:03:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's a waiting line out there
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.68,1:04:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,so they're gonna double and triple it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.68,1:04:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so they close for six
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.03,1:04:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,weeks, reopen,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.03,1:04:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and it goes bankrupt.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.03,1:04:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,In Sedona it happens all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.03,1:04:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, 15, 20 of them I can think of.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.03,1:04:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy of this change.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.92,1:04:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if I were him
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.08,1:04:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I would say in the name of the highest good
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.08,1:04:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,that I double the size of this restaurant
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.08,1:04:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're probably gonna know. Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.08,1:04:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's the ambiance that's pulling the people
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.08,1:04:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and if you double it and make it luxurious
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.08,1:04:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,you've lost what they're there for.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.08,1:04:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I can remember
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.33,1:04:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,in the Gaslight
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.33,1:04:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,District, you know, a very
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.33,1:04:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,popular tavern, you know, very
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.33,1:04:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,popular, everybody goes there.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.33,1:04:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's very cool and hip, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.65,1:04:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to hang out there near the gas
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.65,1:04:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,gasworks. So somebody
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.65,1:04:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,buys it and decides they're gonna clean it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.65,1:04:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They close the
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.65,1:04:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,place for six weeks,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.65,1:04:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,clean it all up, and now nobody goes there.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.65,1:04:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the energy
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.65,1:04:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,is all there. I remember the Electric Circus
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.65,1:05:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,back east in New York.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.65,1:05:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The Electric Circus was one of the first psychedelic
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.65,1:05:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,nightclubs.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.78,1:05:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And rock music, it was very avant-garde.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.78,1:05:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And the cool and the hip went there.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.78,1:05:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And there was a waiting line outside.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.78,1:05:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So they closed it, and of course
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.78,1:05:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,after a couple of years, Andy
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.84,1:05:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Warhol, the whole group used to hang out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.84,1:05:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So they closed it and expanded it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.94,1:05:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And what had been
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.29,1:05:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,really sorta funky
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.68,1:05:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,was now like a white
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.68,1:05:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,alabaster and curved walls.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.68,1:05:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Really weird.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.68,1:05:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,People went
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.68,1:05:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,back there, the acoustics were horrible
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.68,1:05:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,because it bounced off these curved walls.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.68,1:05:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And it went flat broke. Nobody went
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.68,1:05:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,there anymore. But when it was all jammed
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.68,1:05:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,up and funky looking,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.68,1:05:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,it was
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.68,1:05:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,where everybody went, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.87,1:05:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So the thing
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.92,1:05:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to do then is you can pose anything
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.92,1:05:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that you would consider personal,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.92,1:05:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but pose it in a way that is not
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.92,1:05:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,just like you're gonna vote.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.34,1:05:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The way to vote is
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.34,1:06:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,not, I'm always amazed when I hear people
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.34,1:06:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,come on television, they say,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.34,1:06:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,they're gonna vote for so-and-so because he's gonna
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.34,1:06:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,vote for higher wages for truck drivers.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.34,1:06:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the guy's a truck driver.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.10,1:06:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I never hear anybody say, I'm gonna vote for so-and-so
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.10,1:06:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,because I think it's the best for the country.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.10,1:06:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you could say,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.10,1:06:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,which would
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.10,1:06:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,serve the best interest of
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.10,1:06:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,mankind or the country
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.23,1:06:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of just me? I mean, it seems
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.23,1:06:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,to me you would vote for whoever you think is gonna be
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.23,1:06:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the best for the country.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.23,1:06:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And last night on TV, they were saying,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.23,1:06:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, the guy makes pickles and he's gonna vote for
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.23,1:06:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,whoever pays more to pickle
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.23,1:06:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,makers than packers or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.23,1:06:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's so completely
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.23,1:06:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,self-interested. I don't believe
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.23,1:06:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,this that people think in such a petty way.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.23,1:06:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, only me, me, me.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.23,1:06:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's the ego,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.23,1:06:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,egocentricity, and
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.23,1:06:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,it looks to gain.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.23,1:06:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, it's always looking, it's demanding
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.23,1:06:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and it looks to gain.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.12,1:06:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And, alright,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.12,1:07:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,so that's, we could spend a whole
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.12,1:07:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,lecture on this, and we used to spend a whole lecture
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.12,1:07:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,on just going over the
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.12,1:07:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,scale of consciousness and the
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.12,1:07:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,incredible implications.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.05,1:07:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,In the United States of
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.05,1:07:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,America,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.11,1:07:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,well, let's go to the next slide. We'll get
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.11,1:07:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,there. Anyway, let's go to the next slide.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.17,1:07:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we'll go to that after a while.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.17,1:07:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,In the
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.17,1:07:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,world, then, 15%
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.17,1:07:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,of the world's population
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.17,1:07:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates over 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.52,1:07:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,15%.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.47,1:07:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If you drop yourself off in the world
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.47,1:07:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,with a parachute, the chances
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.50,1:07:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,are, 85%,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.50,1:07:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that the people around you will be
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.50,1:07:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,non-integrists. As you'll see
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.20,1:07:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,later, you're safer with Coco,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.20,1:07:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the gorilla,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.20,1:07:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,than you are
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.20,1:07:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,in the United States.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.20,1:07:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, only 49%
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.20,1:07:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,of the people calibrate
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.20,1:07:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,below 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.33,1:08:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,In the United States, which calibrates overall at
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.33,1:08:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,421, 51%
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.33,1:08:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,of the people calibrate over 200
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.33,1:08:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and are integrists.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.49,1:08:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's a very interesting development.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.49,1:08:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We, on the scale of
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.59,1:08:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness, we went up to 600
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.59,1:08:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,because
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.59,1:08:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,there are only a half a dozen people on the planet
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.59,1:08:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,at any time, at this time,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.59,1:08:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,that calibrate over 600. So, it's not
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.59,1:08:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,too useful.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.59,1:08:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We do use it in
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.59,1:08:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrating spiritual teachers throughout
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.59,1:08:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,history. They're the only ones that go over 600.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.59,1:08:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nisargadatta Maharaj,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.78,1:08:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,various people like that, up to a thousand.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.78,1:08:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.88,1:08:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,up to 600 is really all
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.88,1:08:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,of it. At 600,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.88,1:08:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the linear dissolves
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.88,1:08:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,into the non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.97,1:08:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And 50% of the
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.97,1:08:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,time, when people hit level 600,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.97,1:08:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,they leave. They leave
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.07,1:08:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,just because.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.07,1:08:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Because,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.07,1:08:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,well,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.07,1:08:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,they leave and
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.07,1:09:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,they just topple over.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.23,1:09:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,At that level, everything, you don't
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.23,1:09:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,need anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.22,1:09:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And everybody around you thinks you need something, but
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.22,1:09:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,that's because they want to keep the body going,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.22,1:09:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,which is their problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.15,1:09:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So, they feed it and make sure you wash it
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.15,1:09:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and all kinds of strange things.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.18,1:09:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So, 600 and up, you're at the mercy
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.18,1:09:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,of the people around you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.88,1:09:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember Ramana Maharshi,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.95,1:09:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramana Maharshi was
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.95,1:09:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,just an ordinary
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.95,1:09:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,religious, ordinarily religious
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.95,1:09:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,person, not unduly.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.95,1:09:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, in teenage
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.95,1:09:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,somewhere, I forget what age,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.11,1:09:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,he suddenly went into a different state
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.11,1:09:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and he fell down and died.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.11,1:09:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He felt himself die.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.11,1:09:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And he did die.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.40,1:09:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And what
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.07,1:09:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,survived was his consciousness, which
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.07,1:09:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,remained silent for several
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.07,1:09:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,years. Anyway, he
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.07,1:09:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,was bitten by all kinds
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.07,1:09:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,of insects, hadn't eaten in weeks, and
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.07,1:10:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,some spiritually advanced
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.07,1:10:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,people discovered his condition
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.07,1:10:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and saw to it that he ate
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.07,1:10:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and various things like that. And he did
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.07,1:10:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,not even speak for two years.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.07,1:10:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is probably a good
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.20,1:10:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.20,1:10:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the subjective
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.92,1:10:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,states. So, we calibrated them even though
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.92,1:10:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,they're unusual. Historically, they're
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.92,1:10:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,cited all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.92,1:10:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Teachers of enlightenment, avatars,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.92,1:10:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,uh,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.08,1:10:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,avatars in 1985.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.08,1:10:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So, these are the
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.08,1:10:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,depictions of
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.08,1:10:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,divinity, Brahma,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.08,1:10:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,uh,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.37,1:10:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and then archangels,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.17,1:10:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,who you gotta be careful of.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.23,1:10:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Archangels calibrate about 50,000 and up.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.23,1:10:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've told the story
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.23,1:10:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,of my own personal evolution.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.23,1:10:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,In the pits of hell,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.23,1:10:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,in the pits of hell,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.36,1:10:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,in the very bottom of hell,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.36,1:10:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,of absolute blackness and forever despair,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.36,1:10:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,a voice arose
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.39,1:11:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,within that said,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.39,1:11:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,if there is a God,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.42,1:11:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask him for help.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.68,1:11:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And then silence
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.74,1:11:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and oblivion.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.74,1:11:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the explosion
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.00,1:11:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,of the wondrous state
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.00,1:11:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,which revealed divinity
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.03,1:11:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,as creation itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.03,1:11:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only as source, but as creation.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.03,1:11:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.60,1:11:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,then the mind was like
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.14,1:11:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,shock silent in awe.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.14,1:11:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It is still silent in awe.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.33,1:11:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you gotta be careful
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.33,1:11:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,of archangels,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.29,1:11:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,because I always pictured
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.29,1:11:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,that it was a cruising archangel, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.29,1:11:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And here's this idiot in the depths of hell,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.42,1:11:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,says, I ask him if there is a God.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.42,1:11:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And he just glances over like,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.42,1:11:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,hmm, bang.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.25,1:11:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Archangel, 50,000 and up.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.25,1:11:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're talking about
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.25,1:11:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,a logarithmic scale.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.25,1:11:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You can imagine what 50,000 is.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.32,1:12:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,10 times 10 times 10, 50,000 times
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.32,1:12:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the power is so infinite,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.32,1:12:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,it's incomprehensible.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.32,1:12:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The power there is absolute.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.32,1:12:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of the
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.38,1:12:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,absoluteness of the power
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.38,1:12:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,that
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.15,1:12:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the unmanifest
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.04,1:12:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes manifest.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.04,1:12:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The creation,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.14,1:12:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,which is merely a thought,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.14,1:12:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,then begins to unfold.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.52,1:12:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Creation and evolution are one and the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.52,1:12:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the way creation
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.52,1:12:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,presents itself
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.52,1:12:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,seems sequential
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.52,1:12:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and evolutionary.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.52,1:12:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's not evolutionary
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.80,1:12:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,what's evolutionary
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.38,1:12:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,is the witness.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.38,1:12:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What is sequential is the witnessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.89,1:12:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you witness evolution
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.89,1:12:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and it seems to be sequential,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.89,1:12:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,you think evolution is sequential.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.89,1:12:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a total oneness.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.89,1:12:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It is neither sequential
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.89,1:12:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,nor does it even occur within time,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.02,1:12:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,which is the programming
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.02,1:13:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,which the mind projects on the phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.34,1:13:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go away from that.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.34,1:13:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The calibrated levels of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.76,1:13:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,this is their equivalent
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.79,1:13:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,in microwatts.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.79,1:13:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So as you see,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.79,1:13:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,below level,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.79,1:13:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness level 200,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.79,1:13:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the power is limited,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.79,1:13:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,very limited.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.79,1:13:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And then as your consciousness advances,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.79,1:13:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,your power becomes extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.79,1:13:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so we'll move on.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.79,1:13:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the equivalent in microwatts.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.11,1:13:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,85% of the world lives
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.11,1:13:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,below consciousness level 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.11,1:13:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So the great volume
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.11,1:13:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of humanity then
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.11,1:13:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is below
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.11,1:13:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,level 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.84,1:13:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you get
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.84,1:13:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,that this is not a celestial realm?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.84,1:13:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Walmart has
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.16,1:13:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,vaults. I agree.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.16,1:13:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Government officials
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.59,1:13:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,are human. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.59,1:13:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.20,1:14:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not a celestial realm
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.20,1:14:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,where no such phenomena occur.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.20,1:14:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.36,1:14:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why doesn't mankind self-destruct?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.36,1:14:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of the exponential power.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.36,1:14:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The 15%
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.36,1:14:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,have so much power
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.36,1:14:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that they totally counterbalance
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.36,1:14:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,95%.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.73,1:14:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The power, the 15%.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.73,1:14:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So the kindly, loving, forgiving
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.73,1:14:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,thoughts that you have,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.56,1:14:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not conscious of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.56,1:14:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But that is counterbalancing
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.56,1:14:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,980 people
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.27,1:14:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,thinking of suicide
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.40,1:14:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,who suddenly at the last moment
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.40,1:14:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,think, oh,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.75,1:14:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe I'll give it another try.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.78,1:14:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of the presence
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.78,1:14:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,of the infinite power
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.78,1:14:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,of this field.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.78,1:14:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And as a consequence
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.26,1:14:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,of what they are,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.26,1:14:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,what they have become,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.26,1:14:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,counterbalances.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.74,1:14:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what they do,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.74,1:15:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,people think, well, we'll have a peace parade.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.51,1:15:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It's what you have become
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.51,1:15:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,that is the power
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.51,1:15:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that counterbalances.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.63,1:15:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What you do is relatively
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.63,1:15:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.66,1:15:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What you do is only a consequence
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.66,1:15:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,of what you have become anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.66,1:15:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What you have become.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.66,1:15:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So consciousness is like a light bulb
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.66,1:15:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and the higher the level of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.66,1:15:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,the more intense the light
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.66,1:15:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that it shines out.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.92,1:15:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The more intense the light that it shines out.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.36,1:15:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's the next one?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.36,1:15:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we got there already.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.11,1:15:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to the evolution
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.11,1:15:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness over time?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.11,1:15:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The time graph.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.11,1:15:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that was supposed to be next.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.11,1:15:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We can live without it.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.20,1:15:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.84,1:15:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we got a little bit out of step.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.84,1:15:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This was sent by a man named,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.84,1:15:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,it's easy to remember his name.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.84,1:16:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,An engineering student.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.55,1:16:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This suddenly appeared in the mail.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.22,1:16:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as the previous graph.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.22,1:16:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is Daniel Lyons.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.22,1:16:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that an easy one to remember?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.22,1:16:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I always think of Daniel
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.57,1:16:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and the lion's den.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.57,1:16:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy's name is Daniel Lyons.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.57,1:16:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is an adorable name.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.57,1:16:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And he sent this to us.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.57,1:16:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a mathematician,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.57,1:16:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,an engineering student.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.57,1:16:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how much
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.99,1:16:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,evolutionary time
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.99,1:16:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,has elapsed.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.99,1:16:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And you see the
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.99,1:16:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrated level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.99,1:16:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only in the last flick of time
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.05,1:16:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that the calibrated
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.05,1:16:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.05,1:16:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,is now up to
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.05,1:16:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,207 or so.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.31,1:16:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It took this much
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.50,1:16:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,evolutionary time,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.50,1:16:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,eons and eons,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.50,1:16:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,before it even moved off the carpet.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.72,1:17:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It barely got off the carpet
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.72,1:17:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,after eons and eons
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.72,1:17:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.40,1:17:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.40,1:17:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,beginning to rise.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.40,1:17:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,People say, what do you think is the future of mankind?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.40,1:17:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I say, all I can do is look at this graph
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.40,1:17:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and from this graph it looks like
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.40,1:17:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the consciousness of mankind
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.40,1:17:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,is about to catapult ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.72,1:17:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, learning kinesiology
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.72,1:17:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and how to tell truth from falsehood
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.72,1:17:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and all that we lecture about
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.72,1:17:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,is a consequence of this.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.16,1:17:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a consequence of the evolution of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.16,1:17:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that we're now able to tell truth from falsehood
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.16,1:17:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and do so in a second
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.16,1:17:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,about anything, anywhere in time.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.16,1:17:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Or history.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.12,1:17:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So long as the question is
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.12,1:17:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,integrous and the people asking it are integrous.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.12,1:17:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So here's where we are
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.12,1:17:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and you could
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.12,1:17:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,pretty much predict.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.12,1:17:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The nature of consciousness itself
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.12,1:17:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,is to evolve.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.12,1:17:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So now we'll move to the next slide.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.60,1:17:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.40,1:18:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we gotta go backwards to evolutionary time.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.40,1:18:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I got those backwards.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.40,1:18:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, okay, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.40,1:18:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my fault
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.40,1:18:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,because I changed all these charts
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.40,1:18:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,yesterday and
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.40,1:18:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Betty was trying to keep up with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.23,1:18:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,How does this start here?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.23,1:18:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.23,1:18:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I have all kinds of pointers
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.23,1:18:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and of course they're all home.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.16,1:18:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll be the pointer.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.75,1:18:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The beginning of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.07,1:18:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The beginning of the evolution of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.07,1:18:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How did consciousness evolve?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.07,1:18:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This is critical
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.39,1:18:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,to understand from a spiritual
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.39,1:18:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,viewpoint. I'll tell you why.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.39,1:18:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.39,1:18:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, look at that. Right out of the mystical
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.39,1:18:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,wonderment of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.39,1:18:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How did I do that, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.39,1:19:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Intention manifests
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.76,1:19:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,when the conditions are appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.76,1:19:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You see,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.76,1:19:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,how he and I and the pointer and the audience
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.76,1:19:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,are all one concordance.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.76,1:19:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all one concordance
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.76,1:19:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and of course this evolves
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.76,1:19:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,when it's needed.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.63,1:19:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is crucial to understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.20,1:19:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not academic at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.23,1:19:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Self-hatred, guilt, all this stuff
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.23,1:19:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that comes about from egocentricity.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.23,1:19:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hating yourself,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.23,1:19:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,shame, guilt, all that.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.23,1:19:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all a response
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.44,1:19:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to our perceptions,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.44,1:19:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritually evolved people,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.44,1:19:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,our perception of the ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.44,1:19:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you understand the
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.44,1:19:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,evolution of the ego and its core,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.44,1:19:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the essence of it, you stop feeling guilty
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.44,1:19:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,about it. Now you can
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.72,1:19:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,transcend it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.58,1:20:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The first signs of life, the unmanifest
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.58,1:20:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes manifest.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.58,1:20:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So the universe evolves
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.58,1:20:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,as a physicality.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.61,1:20:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What is to become planet Earth
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.61,1:20:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,is liquid lava,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.61,1:20:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,no, just energy flying around
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.61,1:20:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,which condenses itself
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.61,1:20:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,because E equals MC squared
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.61,1:20:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,to the potential
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.61,1:20:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,for
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.68,1:20:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,what do you call
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.67,1:20:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,our galaxy and then
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.67,1:20:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,a little glob of it spins out
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.67,1:20:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,of these hot gases and it condenses
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.67,1:20:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,to lava. And over the
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.70,1:20:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,eons this then cools
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.70,1:20:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,off enough to develop a crust
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.70,1:20:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,on it that could sustain
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.12,1:20:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,life. The interaction
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.34,1:20:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.34,1:20:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the interaction of the
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.34,1:20:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,infinite power of the unmanifest
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.34,1:20:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,when it interacts
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.34,1:20:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,with matter is that it can
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.34,1:20:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,spawn the emergence of life.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.34,1:20:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So the source of life
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.37,1:20:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,is consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.56,1:20:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The source of life is
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.56,1:21:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,non-physical. The source
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.39,1:21:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,of life is
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.39,1:21:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the impact of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.39,1:21:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,on material when
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.39,1:21:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,conditions are
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.39,1:21:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,appropriate for this.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.87,1:21:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That takes care of the mechanistic reductionist.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.87,1:21:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Life does not
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.92,1:21:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,arise from non-life.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.08,1:21:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You see the imbecility of such
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.08,1:21:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,a proposition. That's what's
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.08,1:21:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,called mixing paradigms.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.08,1:21:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mixing levels of abstraction.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.08,1:21:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Violating the Kantian
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.15,1:21:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,categories. It's
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.43,1:21:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,dumb.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.43,1:21:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Life has completely
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.81,1:21:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,different qualities from non-life.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.81,1:21:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The mundane mechanical
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.68,1:21:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,chemical
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.68,1:21:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,cannot create something of a
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.68,1:21:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,totally different level of
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.68,1:21:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,being, existence, paradigm.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.68,1:21:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a violation even within
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.68,1:21:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the Newtonian world of
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.68,1:21:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,logic. What happened to, oh my
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.68,1:22:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,god, I said
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.68,1:22:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,something wrong, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.68,1:22:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I say somebody
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.80,1:22:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,was feeling blue or what happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.80,1:22:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, without
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.63,1:22:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that, folks,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.04,1:22:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,we had a good prognosis for a
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.04,1:22:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,while, but I've got the
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.67,1:22:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,transparency with me if the worst
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.67,1:22:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,comes to worst.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.99,1:22:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,She can play with that. We'll get it back then.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.99,1:22:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.24,1:22:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, the computer world, I stay away
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.24,1:22:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,from it as far as I can.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.24,1:22:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a trap. Once it gets you by
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.24,1:22:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the ankle, you can't get
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.24,1:22:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,loose on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.24,1:22:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, so the evolution of
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.76,1:22:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,life then. Somewhere back in
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.76,1:22:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,infinite time.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.30,1:22:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Unmanifest as
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.46,1:22:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the power of
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.46,1:22:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness itself, the infinite field of
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.46,1:22:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness, interacted
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.46,1:22:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,with material matter
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.46,1:22:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and activated
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.46,1:23:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy of life.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.46,1:23:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, life as it first
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.68,1:23:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,appeared on this crusty
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.68,1:23:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,planet
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.68,1:23:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,did not emerge
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.68,1:23:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,under favorable conditions.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.68,1:23:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, if you landed
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.68,1:23:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,on Mars, your survival
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.68,1:23:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,would be dependent on
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.68,1:23:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,getting energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.68,1:23:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So life is born
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.83,1:23:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,without the source of energy
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.83,1:23:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,within it, it has to get it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.83,1:23:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So the first organism that arose
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.83,1:23:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,was the bacteria.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.83,1:23:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Bacteria calibrate as one.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.83,1:23:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That moved on to
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.92,1:23:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,protozoa, calibrate
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.92,1:23:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,as three. Then on into
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.92,1:23:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the insect world.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.92,1:23:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can see the basic quality of life
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.92,1:23:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is that
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.92,1:23:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the organism has to go
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.92,1:23:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,outside of itself for the energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.92,1:23:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And our
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.05,1:23:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,bad karma as humans
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.05,1:23:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,is that we're not born green.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.05,1:23:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.63,1:23:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,we need chlorophyll instead of skin.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.63,1:24:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,When I get back there to the other side
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.63,1:24:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna tell them too.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.63,1:24:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time you do it,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.64,1:24:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,boss, how about making us green, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.64,1:24:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're green,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.46,1:24:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't need a job, you don't need money,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.46,1:24:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have to go to work.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.91,1:24:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You just walk around being who you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.91,1:24:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Happily,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.36,1:24:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,your green energy
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.36,1:24:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,creates energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.36,1:24:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, in the animal world
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.58,1:24:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,unfortunately,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.64,1:24:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to get.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.64,1:24:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So the core of the ego
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.77,1:24:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,is self-interest.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.87,1:24:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The core of the ego
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.87,1:24:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,is get.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.87,1:24:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And you see the appeal to the voters
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.87,1:24:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,today is based on the same
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.87,1:24:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,get. It's a solar plexus
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.87,1:24:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,energy. Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.96,1:24:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the organism
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.96,1:24:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,is born, it does not
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.96,1:24:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,have within itself
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.96,1:24:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the capacity to create energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.96,1:24:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So the animal kingdom
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.96,1:25:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,has to get it from somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.96,1:25:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And the easiest way is
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.96,1:25:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,to eat it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.12,1:25:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're born to eat.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.12,1:25:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Without eating you die.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.12,1:25:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you were green
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.22,1:25:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,you wouldn't have to eat.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.22,1:25:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You see what a break that would be?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.73,1:25:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's all go together.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.73,1:25:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time we'll come back green
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.73,1:25:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,in a different place.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.73,1:25:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to go to work.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.73,1:25:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to save up money.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.88,1:25:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What good would money be?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.88,1:25:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So the core of the ego then
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.88,1:25:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness level below 200
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.88,1:25:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is get. Selfishness.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.88,1:25:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Self-centeredness.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.88,1:25:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.14,1:25:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,oh goody.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.65,1:25:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the core
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.65,1:25:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,of your animal.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.75,1:25:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside of you is an animal.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.75,1:25:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And here's how the animal grew.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.42,1:25:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at time.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.42,1:25:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember that thing about time?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.42,1:25:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It did nothing forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.42,1:26:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just recently jumped up.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.42,1:26:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So these ages are so old
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.42,1:26:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't pronounce all these words.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.42,1:26:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Trillions and quadrillions
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.42,1:26:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,of rock ages
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.64,1:26:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and things.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.18,1:26:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Bacteria at one.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.18,1:26:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In vertebrates.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.18,1:26:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you get scorpions, snails,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.18,1:26:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,fish, amphibians,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.18,1:26:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,reptiles.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.28,1:26:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally you get up to the dinosaurs.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.28,1:26:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Dinosaurs calibrate at 60.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.04,1:26:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.54,1:26:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,World leaders in every day's headlines.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.54,1:26:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to hold somebody in line.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.70,1:26:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He calibrates over 60.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.91,1:26:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.31,1:27:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been loud, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.04,1:27:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does he calibrate lower than a dinosaur?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.04,1:27:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the dinosaur
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.64,1:27:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,is innocent.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.64,1:27:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It eats the living
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.64,1:27:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,because it has to
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.72,1:27:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,for its own survival.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.76,1:27:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So the dinosaur's intention
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.76,1:27:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,is innocent.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.01,1:27:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The dinosaur's intention
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.01,1:27:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,is merely to eat.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.00,1:27:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And something below 60 then
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.00,1:27:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,would have to be a pretty negative intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.00,1:27:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, that's just an
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.16,1:27:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,accidental thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.42,1:27:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we have the reptiles.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.42,1:27:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And here we have the
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.42,1:27:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,higher dinosaurs.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.42,1:27:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we have modern mammals.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.42,1:27:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And the rise and dominance
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.35,1:27:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,of man. So here you see
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.35,1:27:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,how consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.64,1:27:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,evolved protoplasmically
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.64,1:27:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,as needing.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.64,1:27:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Needful.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.67,1:27:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore you don't have to feel guilty.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.67,1:27:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That your ego
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.67,1:28:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,is greedy.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.67,1:28:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it's greedy.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.67,1:28:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If it wasn't greedy you wouldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.66,1:28:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We owe our survival to the animal within us.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.66,1:28:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And I call the
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.66,1:28:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,animal in me ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.66,1:28:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.66,1:28:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we know that ego hates anybody
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.66,1:28:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,who cuts in on traffic
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.66,1:28:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and that they should die.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.09,1:28:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He knows that the voters
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.09,1:28:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,who are going to vote wrongly
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.18,1:28:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,deserve what they get
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.53,1:28:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,because they're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.80,1:28:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.80,1:28:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,to win it's okay to lie.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.89,1:28:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay to lie to win.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.89,1:28:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he thinks survival
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.89,1:28:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,depends on winning and getting and gaining
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.89,1:28:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and have power over others.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.89,1:28:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why anybody would
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.95,1:28:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,want power over others is totally beyond me.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.46,1:28:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,To control other people, force them to think
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.46,1:29:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the way you think.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.94,1:29:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And when the temptation came
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.94,1:29:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,because it was of an extremely high
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.94,1:29:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,space beyond mind and
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.94,1:29:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,thinkingness and mentalization
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.58,1:29:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,there was really nothing left
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.58,1:29:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,other than the source of life itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.58,1:29:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And there came to me
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.73,1:29:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,so that I understood
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.73,1:29:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,what came to Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.73,1:29:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There comes to you in the silence
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.96,1:29:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,a knowingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.96,1:29:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a knowingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.96,1:29:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a silent transmission.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.96,1:29:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like what? Telepathic I guess.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.96,1:29:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Telepathic.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.27,1:29:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you know that you
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.27,1:29:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,have transcended karma
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.27,1:29:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,now that you know you're not answering
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.27,1:29:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the answer bolt.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.27,1:29:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That there is no God who will
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.27,1:29:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,punish you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.27,1:29:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no consequences for all actions.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.27,1:29:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All power is yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.59,1:29:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Own it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.59,1:29:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.91,1:29:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw what Christ said there
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.91,1:29:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,because there aren't too many people
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.13,1:30:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,at that high pass.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.13,1:30:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And he turned it down.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.44,1:30:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And a few others I saw were there
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.40,1:30:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,turned it down.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.95,1:30:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And happily I saw
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.95,1:30:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,who would want power over others.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.95,1:30:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I turned it down.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.95,1:30:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Own it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.95,1:30:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And all power is yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.84,1:30:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Own it and all power is yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.84,1:30:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there is no payment.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.84,1:30:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're even beyond love.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.84,1:30:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Even beyond love.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.84,1:30:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So you would not even be constrained
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.84,1:30:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,by love.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.84,1:30:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You could put all the poor widows
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.84,1:30:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,out of your apartment house
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.84,1:30:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and double the rent.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.84,1:30:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And if they starved to death
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.23,1:30:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,because you no longer have love for others
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.23,1:30:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you're beyond love.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.23,1:30:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond love is an error
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.09,1:30:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,because love is one of the attributes
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.09,1:30:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.09,1:30:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And a teaching that
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.12,1:30:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,negates love as
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.12,1:30:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,only a manipulation
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.12,1:31:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,or wanting other people's approval
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.12,1:31:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,is a very serious
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.12,1:31:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,very serious error.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.12,1:31:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,180 serious error.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.51,1:31:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is one of the qualities of divinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.51,1:31:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you look at yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.72,1:31:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,you can say
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.72,1:31:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,what do I want with power over others?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.72,1:31:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What a drag it would be wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.24,1:31:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be a drag?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.24,1:31:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That power over others
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.24,1:31:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,control how they think
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.24,1:31:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and what they believe and all that.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.24,1:31:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.12,1:31:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,we see the rise and dominance of man
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.41,1:31:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and we see
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.41,1:31:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and we saw from that previous chart
Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.41,1:31:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,that it's only about now.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.41,1:31:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay so move on to the next slide.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.41,1:31:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What say?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.55,1:31:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She thinks for me, thank God.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.38,1:31:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back, let's go to the next one.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.89,1:31:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay and
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.89,1:31:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,very interestingly
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.89,1:31:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,this is one of my favorite slides
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.89,1:31:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and after you've seen this slide
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.89,1:32:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and comprehend it
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.89,1:32:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,it will eliminate guilt forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.89,1:32:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Guilt, shame,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.89,1:32:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,hatred
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.89,1:32:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,you get rid of it all now forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.89,1:32:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Because once you understand
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.89,1:32:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the core of the narcissist
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.89,1:32:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,is the ego that you were born with.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.89,1:32:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You were born with an animal brain
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.89,1:32:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,that's your hardware.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.89,1:32:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Karmically you come in with software
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.89,1:32:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but that software now has to play on this hardware.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.89,1:32:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're stuck with biologic hardware of an animal folks.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.44,1:32:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.44,1:32:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We own our animal.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.75,1:32:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The way we disappeared is
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.75,1:32:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,we stopped making an enemy of them
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.75,1:32:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and we say yeah I've got an animal nature.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.96,1:32:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So here we see the protozoa.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.96,1:32:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We see
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.96,1:32:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,oh I've got a pointer now.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.96,1:32:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And look
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.32,1:32:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,this is really fun.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.32,1:32:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You see how they all come up here?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.32,1:32:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Crustaceans, insects,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.38,1:32:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,grasshoppers. Here's grasshoppers.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.38,1:32:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not too smart, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.51,1:32:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But they're still around.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.51,1:33:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Reptiles,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.83,1:33:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,snakes, alligators.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.83,1:33:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. I don't understand people
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.86,1:33:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,who play with alligators.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.86,1:33:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just macho that you can grab an alligator
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.86,1:33:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,get your picture taken.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.86,1:33:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to see them grab a dinosaur though.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.21,1:33:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see you do that one.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.21,1:33:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Or a Komodo dragon.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.21,1:33:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And we see whales
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.31,1:33:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and dolphins,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.31,1:33:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,migratory birds, birds of prey,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.31,1:33:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,rhinoceros,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.37,1:33:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,songbirds, doves.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.37,1:33:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And polar bear,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.50,1:33:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,water buffalo. Water buffalo are
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.50,1:33:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,very dangerous. Water buffalo
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.50,1:33:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,will be staying there and then just suddenly for no reason
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.50,1:33:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll charge you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.46,1:33:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's not as dangerous as the hippopotamus.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.46,1:33:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And I always tell people about the hippopotamus.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.46,1:33:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Kills more humans than any other
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.46,1:33:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,wild animal. Do not hang
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.81,1:33:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,out with hippopotamus if you get nothing else
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.81,1:33:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,out of this lecture.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.81,1:33:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You see these idiots in canoes
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.68,1:33:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,are hanging out with hippopotamus.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.68,1:33:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally he says
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.68,1:34:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Four people plus a canoe
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.68,1:34:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,go down his goal.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.67,1:34:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do not hang out.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.67,1:34:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You see there's people that haven't even gotten
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.67,1:34:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,that far. Do not hang out
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.67,1:34:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,with hippopotamus.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.52,1:34:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not lay down on the railroad track.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.52,1:34:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.30,1:34:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you see the emergence of the grazers.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.30,1:34:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And much to our surprise when we calibrated these
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.30,1:34:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,we saw suddenly we had
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.30,1:34:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,gone over consciousness level 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.30,1:34:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the critical level
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.30,1:34:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,in the human. And wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.30,1:34:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is. The critical level
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.30,1:34:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,characteristic difference between
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.30,1:34:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,animals below 200 and animals
Dialogue: 0,1:34:40.30,1:34:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,over 200. Below
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.30,1:34:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,200 they live at the price of the life
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.30,1:34:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,of others. They have
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.30,1:34:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to eat and kill
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.30,1:34:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to live. And now
Dialogue: 0,1:34:50.30,1:34:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,at 200 suddenly you become benign.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:52.30,1:34:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like the human dimension.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.30,1:34:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Below 200 people are dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.56,1:34:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not safe till
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.56,1:35:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,they're 200 and over.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.23,1:35:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And the animal kingdom, you see the same
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.23,1:35:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,phenomena. Isn't that curious?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.23,1:35:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness level 200
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.23,1:35:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,then differentiates. That
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.23,1:35:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,which is dangerous
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.42,1:35:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and that which is benign.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.42,1:35:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So the animal once it reaches
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.42,1:35:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,200 becomes a grazer.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.42,1:35:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It eats grass. It doesn't kill
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.42,1:35:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,anybody. It doesn't tear them to pieces.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.42,1:35:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.42,1:35:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you see they'll defend themselves
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.42,1:35:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,like an elephant. You get up
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.42,1:35:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to cats at 240. Family
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.42,1:35:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,cat 245. So when
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.42,1:35:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you adopt a pet
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.42,1:35:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,just their being around you
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.42,1:35:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,advances their consciousness 5
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.42,1:35:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,sometimes even 10 points.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.42,1:35:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Family dog you see.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.42,1:35:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Monkeys, gorillas, chimpanzees.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.42,1:35:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And here's
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.19,1:35:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,an African Grey.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.40,1:35:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Alex. Alex
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.47,1:35:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,is Broccoli's
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.66,1:35:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,ideal.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.81,1:35:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep listening
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.81,1:36:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,pretty soon you'll be smart as Alex.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.81,1:36:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be smart
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.13,1:36:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,as Alex.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:05.13,1:36:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Grey is named Broccoli.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.13,1:36:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So we've been calibrating Broccoli every couple of months.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.13,1:36:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Coco. We all know
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.13,1:36:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Coco. Coco is
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.13,1:36:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,really quite benign.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:15.13,1:36:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're safer with Coco
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.13,1:36:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,a gorilla than most
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.13,1:36:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,of the people on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.13,1:36:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Coco is at 405.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.29,1:36:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we see the
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.29,1:36:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,wonderment of these two pets.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.29,1:36:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We see that the cat's purr
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.29,1:36:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates at
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.29,1:36:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,500 and the dog's wagging tail
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.29,1:36:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates at 500.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.29,1:36:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,500 is love.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.29,1:36:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So the dog's wagging tail
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.29,1:36:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the cat's purr
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.29,1:36:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,is reflecting the
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.29,1:36:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,energy of love.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.29,1:36:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll just tell the last story when we were in Toronto
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.29,1:36:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we'll take a break.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.29,1:36:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And when we were in Toronto
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.29,1:36:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,on the front page of the paper
Dialogue: 0,1:36:53.29,1:36:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the day we gave the lecture
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.29,1:36:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,was the story of a dog named Elvis.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.29,1:36:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And Elvis, there was a man in the park
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.29,1:37:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,who had
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.29,1:37:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,6,000 rounds of ammo
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.29,1:37:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and high powered rifles
Dialogue: 0,1:37:05.29,1:37:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and he was like the famous
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.29,1:37:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,killers that hit the newsreel
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.29,1:37:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,gonna mow down everybody, kill everybody
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.29,1:37:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and then kill himself.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.29,1:37:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He would not give up his weapons.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.52,1:37:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He would not give up his weapons.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.52,1:37:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,All of a sudden
Dialogue: 0,1:37:20.06,1:37:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Elvis, this dog
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.06,1:37:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,ran across with a
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.06,1:37:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,frisbee in his mouth
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.06,1:37:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and jumped up and wanted this
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.06,1:37:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,guy to play.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.06,1:37:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And this guy suddenly came to his senses
Dialogue: 0,1:37:32.06,1:37:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly said, what the hell am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.06,1:37:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And dropped his
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.06,1:37:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,rifle and surrendered to the
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.06,1:37:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,officials and I guess he's now in treatment.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.06,1:37:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But see Elvis came up
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.06,1:37:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,with an energy fuel to 500
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.06,1:37:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,so his wagging tail
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.06,1:37:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,his 500
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.06,1:37:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,hit this man's dementia
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.06,1:37:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and the man became sane.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.06,1:37:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.06,1:37:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The healing power of love which we know
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.06,1:37:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,experientially
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.22,1:38:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,in therapeutics.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.22,1:38:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We know that people who have dogs and cats
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.22,1:38:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,or pets and love them
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.22,1:38:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,live longer, have lower blood pressure
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.22,1:38:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,have fewer heart attacks, etc.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:08.22,1:38:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't mean that you can't get out of here
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.22,1:38:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but they'll
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.22,1:38:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,they'll make the way
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.22,1:38:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,waiting time more pleasant.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.22,1:38:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sitting on the park bench
Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.22,1:38:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,waiting to leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.22,1:38:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have your kitty purring in your lap
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.22,1:38:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and when you leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.22,1:38:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,When it's time to leave the planet
Dialogue: 0,1:38:26.22,1:38:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,all I want is the cat and the kitty
Dialogue: 0,1:38:28.22,1:38:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and the surrounding
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.22,1:38:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,being surrounded by love.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.22,1:38:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Love tends to bring
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.22,1:38:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,love to oneself. So loving people
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.22,1:38:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I think tend to have loving pets.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.22,1:38:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're going to take a break for how long?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.22,1:38:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifteen minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.25,1:38:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifteen minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.25,1:38:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:50.81,1:38:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the sound person?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.70,1:38:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Sound person.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.95,1:38:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sound person.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.95,1:39:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the sound person?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.21,1:39:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We know that a fifteen minute break
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.21,1:39:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,always takes half an hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.21,1:39:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we give you fifteen minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.21,1:39:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If we gave you half an hour
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.56,1:39:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,it would take forty-five.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.56,1:39:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Now in all the excitement here
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.56,1:39:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot what today's lecture was about.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.54,1:39:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But now I remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.72,1:39:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's lecture is called
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.72,1:39:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We said the human mind
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.12,1:39:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,cannot move faster than
Dialogue: 0,1:39:38.12,1:39:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,one ten-thousandth of a second.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.19,1:39:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, how are you going to
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.19,1:39:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,discover
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.19,1:39:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,this field here?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.41,1:39:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,When
Dialogue: 0,1:39:52.19,1:39:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,in early life, teenage or whatever it was
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.19,1:39:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I caught the
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.02,1:39:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,mind claiming credit
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.02,1:40:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,for saving the life of the rabbit.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.31,1:40:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't the mind that did that.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.31,1:40:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't the mind that did that.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.76,1:40:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the field.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.14,1:40:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The field.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.24,1:40:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where the first mind arises.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.88,1:40:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The witness observer.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.03,1:40:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,People want to know how to become enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.03,1:40:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I tell them.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.51,1:40:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop identifying with content
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.51,1:40:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and identify with the field.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.73,1:40:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Because meditation is something that
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.73,1:40:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,tends to be somewhat artificial.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.05,1:40:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not what you do in everyday life.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.05,1:40:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of people go someplace
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.05,1:40:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and pay money to learn it
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.05,1:40:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and spend three weeks learning it.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.43,1:40:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're very enthused about meditation.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.43,1:40:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So you do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.84,1:40:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it myself for an hour in the morning
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.84,1:40:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and night for many years.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.07,1:40:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And then what happens is
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.07,1:40:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,your life gets to be too busy.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.07,1:40:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And so now you do it for half an hour
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.07,1:40:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you skip Monday morning
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.07,1:40:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and then Thursday night you forget it.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.07,1:41:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And within six months you've given up meditation.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.89,1:41:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you go to a retreat
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.89,1:41:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and you do it again for a week.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.88,1:41:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's not something that you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.88,1:41:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.95,1:41:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,in addition
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.36,1:41:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,compartmentalized.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.46,1:41:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll go and meditate now.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.46,1:41:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It means you've got to leave everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.46,1:41:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Get off the TV.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.49,1:41:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell the dog
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.49,1:41:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,go lay down.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.16,1:41:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to go to some special place.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.16,1:41:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a special mat.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.42,1:41:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Special perfume, incense,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:31.42,1:41:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,all kinds of images of divine figures.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.42,1:41:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You go into this state.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.41,1:41:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.92,1:41:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And then when you
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.21,1:41:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,stand up and walk around
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.21,1:41:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,back.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.21,1:41:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right back to where you were.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:53.52,1:41:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness is advanced by
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.52,1:41:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,identifying with the field.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.71,1:41:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Not with the content of the field
Dialogue: 0,1:41:59.71,1:42:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,but with the field itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.84,1:42:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the witness observer.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.84,1:42:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,See.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.93,1:42:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind is literal and linear
Dialogue: 0,1:42:09.21,1:42:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's good for
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.21,1:42:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,figuring out what all the controls are
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.21,1:42:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,in the car, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:15.69,1:42:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a new Chevy
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.69,1:42:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's got 100 controls.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:19.69,1:42:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,100 controls.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.69,1:42:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,At my age that's a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.84,1:42:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the on
Dialogue: 0,1:42:27.13,1:42:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,or off?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.77,1:42:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:31.80,1:42:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go see these
Dialogue: 0,1:42:33.80,1:42:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and then see these playing when I'm driving.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.80,1:42:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have run over the rabbit.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.38,1:42:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.38,1:42:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When you drive
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.33,1:42:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you trust the field, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:46.36,1:42:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't just trust what you're looking at
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.36,1:42:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,because this car is just coming in
Dialogue: 0,1:42:50.36,1:42:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,from this side.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.36,1:42:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,When you drive
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.36,1:42:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you tend to spread your consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.36,1:42:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and your awareness to the field.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.36,1:43:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Or you better or you wouldn't be here today.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.36,1:43:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:02.56,1:43:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're aware of the totality.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:09.61,1:43:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're aware of your creative lifestyle
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.64,1:43:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,than this one
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.64,1:43:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,in which
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.52,1:43:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,you become aligned with the field
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.52,1:43:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,rather than the content of the field.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.52,1:43:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll get to a diagram about that later.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:24.81,1:43:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You get to be the field.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:27.04,1:43:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:29.04,1:43:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the field and the observer
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.90,1:43:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,do not move within time.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:33.90,1:43:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind has to move from
Dialogue: 0,1:43:36.32,1:43:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the particular to the particular
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.32,1:43:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,to the particular.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:40.51,1:43:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's confined to the linear
Dialogue: 0,1:43:42.96,1:43:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,so the mind goes from this word
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.96,1:43:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to this picture in the paper
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.96,1:43:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to this TV thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.18,1:43:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So the mind can only move
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.18,1:43:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,can't move any faster than
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.18,1:43:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,one tenth of a second.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:55.24,1:43:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Flicks from this to this.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:57.76,1:43:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The field doesn't move
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.76,1:44:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,from anything to anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:01.76,1:44:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If you become
Dialogue: 0,1:44:03.95,1:44:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,one with the field
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.20,1:44:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the field automatically
Dialogue: 0,1:44:08.20,1:44:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,notices
Dialogue: 0,1:44:10.20,1:44:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,that the brake went on before.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:12.20,1:44:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind took credit.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.20,1:44:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the witness observing
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.56,1:44:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,that discerned that.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.59,1:44:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So the witness observer
Dialogue: 0,1:44:20.59,1:44:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,is faster than
Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.81,1:44:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,one tenth of a second
Dialogue: 0,1:44:24.88,1:44:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,because it is not on and off.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.88,1:44:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't move from this to that.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.88,1:44:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the totality
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.88,1:44:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,of the field.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.91,1:44:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the field that sees all three fish
Dialogue: 0,1:44:34.91,1:44:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,arise out of the sea at once.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:36.97,1:44:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If I look at this fish
Dialogue: 0,1:44:38.97,1:44:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and then this fish
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.77,1:44:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't do it, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:43.77,1:44:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're one with the field
Dialogue: 0,1:44:47.76,1:44:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you see all three fish
Dialogue: 0,1:44:49.76,1:44:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,simultaneously of their own.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.76,1:44:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very obvious.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.01,1:44:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to attend lectures
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.01,1:45:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,to remind you what a flying fish knows.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:01.95,1:45:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It just is what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:05.95,1:45:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't think
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.95,1:45:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,oh I decided to leap out of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:09.95,1:45:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nature
Dialogue: 0,1:45:12.08,1:45:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,did that for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:14.17,1:45:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So the witness observer
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.24,1:45:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'll get to a diagram
Dialogue: 0,1:45:18.24,1:45:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that explains that
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.16,1:45:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,is the field.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.16,1:45:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So I tend to emphasize contemplation
Dialogue: 0,1:45:25.16,1:45:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,as a spiritual style.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:27.93,1:45:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,To be aware of the totality
Dialogue: 0,1:45:29.93,1:45:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,of the field.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:33.34,1:45:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The current political thing is
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.34,1:45:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,it isn't what this one says
Dialogue: 0,1:45:37.53,1:45:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and what this one says.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:39.53,1:45:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what they all focus on.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.53,1:45:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more the intention of the field.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.53,1:45:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the intention of the field?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:45.53,1:45:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the intention of the people involved?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:47.53,1:45:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the overall field
Dialogue: 0,1:45:49.53,1:45:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,that they're creating?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:51.69,1:45:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you try to decide
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.69,1:45:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,which field is the best
Dialogue: 0,1:45:56.27,1:45:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,for the country.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:59.26,1:46:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw a TV
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.26,1:46:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,being interviewed saying
Dialogue: 0,1:46:03.26,1:46:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,they're going to do what's best
Dialogue: 0,1:46:05.26,1:46:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,for the country.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:07.26,1:46:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They're going to do what's best
Dialogue: 0,1:46:09.26,1:46:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,for us truck drivers
Dialogue: 0,1:46:11.26,1:46:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,or us plumbers
Dialogue: 0,1:46:13.45,1:46:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,or us whatever
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.45,1:46:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of the field.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.90,1:46:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,When you ask what
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.90,1:46:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,in the name of the highest good
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.90,1:46:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,so you would ask
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.90,1:46:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,if you want to find out how to vote
Dialogue: 0,1:46:25.90,1:46:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,in the name of the highest good
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.90,1:46:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I would be best serving the highest good
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.90,1:46:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,appeals to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.00,1:46:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go back to the slides.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:36.86,1:46:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We got as far as the dog's wagging tail
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.86,1:46:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and Elvis.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.53,1:46:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to go on to the next one.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:44.46,1:46:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You see the animal now
Dialogue: 0,1:46:46.46,1:46:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you're born with
Dialogue: 0,1:46:48.46,1:46:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that's your physiology.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.39,1:46:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Then on top of this animal brain
Dialogue: 0,1:46:57.45,1:46:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,evolves the prefrontal cortex.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:59.45,1:47:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The prefrontal cortex
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.76,1:47:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,does not replace
Dialogue: 0,1:47:04.76,1:47:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,the animal brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:07.47,1:47:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an add-on.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.11,1:47:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you have the great
Dialogue: 0,1:47:12.11,1:47:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,difficulty of being a human being.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.11,1:47:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If I was St. Peter
Dialogue: 0,1:47:16.49,1:47:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say where have you been? Planet Earth?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:18.49,1:47:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been a human being? Yes. Pass.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:20.49,1:47:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.49,1:47:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're stuck with an animal brain
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.49,1:47:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and a prefrontal cortex
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.49,1:47:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,with spiritual awareness,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.49,1:47:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,honesty, integrity, answerability
Dialogue: 0,1:47:30.49,1:47:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and such things.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:32.49,1:47:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you've got
Dialogue: 0,1:47:34.68,1:47:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,a setup for conflict.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:37.93,1:47:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How to resolve the conflict then
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.93,1:47:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,traditionally has been done
Dialogue: 0,1:47:41.93,1:47:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,the down side, the gothic side
Dialogue: 0,1:47:43.93,1:47:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,of traditional religion
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.93,1:47:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,has been sin and guilt and penance, etc.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:47.93,1:47:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ash cloth,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:50.32,1:47:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,sackcloth and ashes.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:53.60,1:47:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Consequently
Dialogue: 0,1:47:55.88,1:47:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,few people have become enlightened in history.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:57.88,1:47:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an extreme rarity.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.88,1:48:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Because
Dialogue: 0,1:48:01.88,1:48:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,God is not at the bottom of the chart
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.88,1:48:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Calvary of the level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:05.88,1:48:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,God is at the top.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:08.11,1:48:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Joy, happiness, forgiveness
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.11,1:48:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,1:48:12.11,1:48:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the first thing we learn is that
Dialogue: 0,1:48:14.11,1:48:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,God is not at the bottom of the chart
Dialogue: 0,1:48:16.11,1:48:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,God is at the top of the chart.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:18.11,1:48:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Joy, forgiveness
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.11,1:48:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,love.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:23.23,1:48:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What to do with the down side then?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:28.11,1:48:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you
Dialogue: 0,1:48:30.30,1:48:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,vilify it, you set up a duality
Dialogue: 0,1:48:32.30,1:48:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,in which the ego
Dialogue: 0,1:48:37.53,1:48:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes your enemy. Your animal nature
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.53,1:48:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,now becomes your enemy.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:43.55,1:48:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And you have to do penance and say the rosary.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.55,1:48:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it gets angry
Dialogue: 0,1:48:47.74,1:48:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's the
Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.74,1:48:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,selfish, etc.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:52.19,1:48:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The way to eliminate a thing is to not
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.19,1:48:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,resist it and to adopt it.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:56.80,1:48:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You adopt it.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:58.80,1:49:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My ego's name is
Dialogue: 0,1:49:00.80,1:49:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:02.80,1:49:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And I accept
Dialogue: 0,1:49:05.05,1:49:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that ego is what it is
Dialogue: 0,1:49:07.05,1:49:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's my animal inheritance.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:09.05,1:49:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of vilifying it
Dialogue: 0,1:49:11.05,1:49:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I said of course you're selfish.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.05,1:49:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you want to win.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:15.34,1:49:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course people in traffic deserve to die.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.34,1:49:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And the
Dialogue: 0,1:49:19.85,1:49:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,people who vote wrongly, we know who they are.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.85,1:49:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Deserve what they get,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:26.22,1:49:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,don't they?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:28.22,1:49:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So you just
Dialogue: 0,1:49:30.86,1:49:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,assume that the ego is that way
Dialogue: 0,1:49:32.86,1:49:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and that everybody's ego is that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.68,1:49:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So you finally have a prefrontal
Dialogue: 0,1:49:43.68,1:49:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,cortex. So as
Dialogue: 0,1:49:46.44,1:49:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness evolves,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:48.44,1:49:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,it evolves from
Dialogue: 0,1:49:50.57,1:49:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the emotions of
Dialogue: 0,1:49:52.57,1:49:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the negative emotions
Dialogue: 0,1:49:55.08,1:49:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,then it evolves to more positive
Dialogue: 0,1:49:57.08,1:49:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,emotions.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:59.79,1:50:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,At the very bottom it's pure animal emotion.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:01.79,1:50:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it evolves
Dialogue: 0,1:50:03.79,1:50:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,from negative emotions, shame,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:05.79,1:50:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,guilt, hatred, etc.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.79,1:50:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,to positive emotions.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.79,1:50:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Enthusiasm, commitment, reliability,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:11.79,1:50:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the traditional
Dialogue: 0,1:50:13.79,1:50:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,virtues of traditional America.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:15.79,1:50:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And eventually the
Dialogue: 0,1:50:17.92,1:50:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,prefrontal cortex evolves to the point
Dialogue: 0,1:50:19.92,1:50:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,where it can think.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:22.17,1:50:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Most people think they can think but that's
Dialogue: 0,1:50:24.17,1:50:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,an illusion. They're not thinking.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.17,1:50:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They think they're thinking.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:29.07,1:50:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't really
Dialogue: 0,1:50:31.07,1:50:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,think until you get to consciousness level
Dialogue: 0,1:50:33.07,1:50:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,400, which excludes
Dialogue: 0,1:50:35.07,1:50:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,most voters.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:43.77,1:50:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Logic and
Dialogue: 0,1:50:45.77,1:50:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,reason arose late
Dialogue: 0,1:50:47.77,1:50:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,in the game.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:49.87,1:50:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It really hasn't made much
Dialogue: 0,1:50:52.06,1:50:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,progress since about
Dialogue: 0,1:50:54.06,1:50:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,350 BC.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:56.19,1:50:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,In 350 BC, Aristotle,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:58.19,1:51:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Plato, Socrates
Dialogue: 0,1:51:00.19,1:51:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,pretty much, of course later refined
Dialogue: 0,1:51:02.19,1:51:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Kant and others.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.19,1:51:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But pretty much it was said
Dialogue: 0,1:51:06.19,1:51:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the logic, the difference between rhetoric and
Dialogue: 0,1:51:08.19,1:51:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,logic, and the
Dialogue: 0,1:51:10.22,1:51:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,paradigm of reality that
Dialogue: 0,1:51:12.22,1:51:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,dominates our current society.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:14.22,1:51:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,American society calibrates at 421.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:16.22,1:51:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,400 is the level
Dialogue: 0,1:51:19.02,1:51:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,of the intellect,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:21.02,1:51:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,reason, the prefrontal cortex,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:23.02,1:51:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,education, college.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:25.72,1:51:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So America calibrates higher than any country
Dialogue: 0,1:51:27.72,1:51:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,in the world right now at 421.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:29.72,1:51:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So we celebrate
Dialogue: 0,1:51:31.72,1:51:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,inventiveness, creativeness,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:33.72,1:51:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,intelligence,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:35.72,1:51:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,going to college, learning,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:37.72,1:51:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,reading, becoming educated,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:39.72,1:51:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,staying up with current events,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:41.72,1:51:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,being informed.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:43.72,1:51:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So we emphasize
Dialogue: 0,1:51:45.72,1:51:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:47.95,1:51:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And out of it has come a great society.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:49.95,1:51:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A great society.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:53.29,1:51:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Capacity to reason and to think.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:55.29,1:51:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's, this is
Dialogue: 0,1:51:57.48,1:51:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the world I grew up in. In childhood
Dialogue: 0,1:51:59.48,1:52:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,other people were playing stickball and
Dialogue: 0,1:52:01.48,1:52:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,wrestling and all kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:03.48,1:52:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And football and
Dialogue: 0,1:52:05.48,1:52:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,all kinds of dangerous games.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:07.48,1:52:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't allow me on the football field.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:09.48,1:52:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The coach said, I don't want you on the football field
Dialogue: 0,1:52:11.48,1:52:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,because your bones are just going to
Dialogue: 0,1:52:13.48,1:52:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,get crunched. And so he wouldn't
Dialogue: 0,1:52:15.48,1:52:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,approve me for anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:19.48,1:52:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The worst day for me was field day
Dialogue: 0,1:52:21.80,1:52:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,when there was no classes and
Dialogue: 0,1:52:23.80,1:52:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody climbed ropes and did somersaults
Dialogue: 0,1:52:25.80,1:52:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and other nightmarish things.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.48,1:52:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I was into the great books
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.48,1:52:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,of the western world.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:33.12,1:52:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Which were assembled by
Dialogue: 0,1:52:35.21,1:52:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mortimer Adler at the University of Chicago
Dialogue: 0,1:52:37.21,1:52:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,in the 50s.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:39.21,1:52:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the greatest thinkers the world has ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:41.21,1:52:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the people that set up the paradigm
Dialogue: 0,1:52:43.21,1:52:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,of America as it stands today.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:45.21,1:52:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The Constitution
Dialogue: 0,1:52:47.47,1:52:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,of the United States, which calibrates
Dialogue: 0,1:52:49.47,1:52:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,at 710, the highest of any
Dialogue: 0,1:52:51.47,1:52:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,in the world. 710.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:53.53,1:52:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,710. Extremely brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:59.04,1:53:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so terrific about the
Dialogue: 0,1:53:01.04,1:53:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,United States Constitution?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:03.23,1:53:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It says,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:05.23,1:53:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,equality arises
Dialogue: 0,1:53:07.23,1:53:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,by virtue of the
Dialogue: 0,1:53:09.23,1:53:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,divinity of our creator.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:11.23,1:53:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The Americans political
Dialogue: 0,1:53:14.25,1:53:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,rights arise out of
Dialogue: 0,1:53:16.25,1:53:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the fact that out of the creator
Dialogue: 0,1:53:18.25,1:53:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,arose the rights of man.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:20.25,1:53:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Not by the vote.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:22.25,1:53:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Not by secularism.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:24.25,1:53:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Not by one army winning over another.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:26.92,1:53:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But by virtue of the
Dialogue: 0,1:53:28.92,1:53:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,divinity of our source.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:30.92,1:53:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That is what gives us
Dialogue: 0,1:53:33.12,1:53:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,freedom of religion
Dialogue: 0,1:53:35.12,1:53:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and freedom from religion.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:37.12,1:53:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,710.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:39.12,1:53:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Constitution of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:41.12,1:53:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,People that want to meddle with it,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:43.47,1:53:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,when you calibrate them,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:45.47,1:53:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,are usually less than 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:47.47,1:53:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Change the Constitution of the United States,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:49.47,1:53:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,you calibrate that energy of that person,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:51.47,1:53:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,you usually find it's less than 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:53.47,1:53:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the sheer arrogance of it
Dialogue: 0,1:53:55.47,1:53:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,is enough to put you below 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:57.47,1:53:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:59.47,1:54:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,here you've got the greatest minds.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:01.47,1:54:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So, while everybody else is playing stickball
Dialogue: 0,1:54:03.47,1:54:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and other violent games,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:06.01,1:54:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,sticking their fingers in each other's
Dialogue: 0,1:54:08.01,1:54:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,eyes and things,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:10.01,1:54:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sitting
Dialogue: 0,1:54:12.01,1:54:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,with a big book in front of me,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:14.01,1:54:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and I wore very thick glasses,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:16.01,1:54:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I had trifocals and all.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:18.01,1:54:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So here's this skinny ectomorph,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:20.01,1:54:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, a bookworm,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:22.01,1:54:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and the mesomorphs
Dialogue: 0,1:54:24.01,1:54:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,are out there whacking into each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:26.01,1:54:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I could never really get the pleasure of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:28.01,1:54:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the pleasure of wrestling?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:30.01,1:54:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy's eyeballs are
Dialogue: 0,1:54:32.01,1:54:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,in your point.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:34.01,1:54:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the kick out of that?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:36.01,1:54:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:38.11,1:54:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I was fascinated with Aristotle
Dialogue: 0,1:54:40.11,1:54:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and Plato and
Dialogue: 0,1:54:42.56,1:54:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the aphorisms of Marcus Aurelius
Dialogue: 0,1:54:44.56,1:54:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and things like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:46.56,1:54:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see here's in the 400s
Dialogue: 0,1:54:48.56,1:54:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thomas Aquinas and
Dialogue: 0,1:54:50.56,1:54:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Marcus Aurelius,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:52.56,1:54:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Francis Bacon, Berkeley,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:54.56,1:54:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,all the great names of history.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:56.56,1:54:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Chaucer,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:58.56,1:55:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Darwin at 450.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:00.56,1:55:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So here you see the Newtonian paradigm.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:02.56,1:55:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Sir Isaac Newton?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:04.56,1:55:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he's on here too, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:06.56,1:55:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You see the
Dialogue: 0,1:55:09.55,1:55:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,idea of causality.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:11.55,1:55:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the problem with the human mind,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:13.55,1:55:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can't tell truth from falsehood,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:15.55,1:55:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,was delineated quite clearly
Dialogue: 0,1:55:17.68,1:55:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,by Descartes.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:20.80,1:55:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem with the human mind
Dialogue: 0,1:55:23.21,1:55:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,is its dualistic nature.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:25.21,1:55:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It thinks
Dialogue: 0,1:55:27.66,1:55:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,that what res interna,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:29.85,1:55:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,res cogitans,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:31.85,1:55:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,it thinks
Dialogue: 0,1:55:33.85,1:55:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,that what it thinks
Dialogue: 0,1:55:35.85,1:55:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is what is out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:37.88,1:55:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It confuses res interna
Dialogue: 0,1:55:39.88,1:55:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,with res externa.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:42.08,1:55:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The reality of thinkingness
Dialogue: 0,1:55:44.08,1:55:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,with the reality of nature
Dialogue: 0,1:55:46.08,1:55:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,is what the universe is.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:49.20,1:55:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If you follow what I'm saying
Dialogue: 0,1:55:51.71,1:55:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,you will see that
Dialogue: 0,1:55:53.87,1:55:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the concept of causality
Dialogue: 0,1:55:55.87,1:55:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,is res interna,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:57.87,1:55:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,res cogitans.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:59.87,1:56:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a thinkingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:05.29,1:56:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That there is a this causing a that
Dialogue: 0,1:56:07.29,1:56:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,is a dualistic perception
Dialogue: 0,1:56:11.12,1:56:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,on the part of the mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:13.12,1:56:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It now projects it
Dialogue: 0,1:56:15.37,1:56:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,into the world
Dialogue: 0,1:56:17.37,1:56:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and thinks causality is out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:22.67,1:56:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,In thinking that, for one thing,
Dialogue: 0,1:56:24.67,1:56:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,when it comes to causality
Dialogue: 0,1:56:26.89,1:56:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,it's violating a very
Dialogue: 0,1:56:29.12,1:56:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,basic principle of logic itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:31.12,1:56:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Because a thing follows another
Dialogue: 0,1:56:34.56,1:56:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't mean
Dialogue: 0,1:56:36.56,1:56:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,it's caused by that which preceded it.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:38.56,1:56:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the great illusion
Dialogue: 0,1:56:40.56,1:56:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,which science itself falls into.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:42.84,1:56:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So science
Dialogue: 0,1:56:44.84,1:56:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,is limited to the paradigm
Dialogue: 0,1:56:46.84,1:56:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,of about 450 to 460
Dialogue: 0,1:56:48.84,1:56:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,even quantum mechanics.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:52.54,1:56:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,To go beyond duality
Dialogue: 0,1:56:54.54,1:56:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,you then have to go into a different paradigm,
Dialogue: 0,1:56:56.54,1:56:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,a different paradigm.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:58.89,1:57:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Within the Newtonian paradigm
Dialogue: 0,1:57:00.89,1:57:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,of causality.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:02.89,1:57:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're stuck with causality
Dialogue: 0,1:57:04.89,1:57:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,to a spiritual student
Dialogue: 0,1:57:06.89,1:57:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,you're then stuck with the thought
Dialogue: 0,1:57:08.89,1:57:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,that there is a personal separate I
Dialogue: 0,1:57:10.89,1:57:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,causing a that.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:17.47,1:57:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a personal I.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:20.14,1:57:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's answerable, punishable,
Dialogue: 0,1:57:23.32,1:57:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,limited.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:26.99,1:57:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And it causes that.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:28.99,1:57:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It decides that.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:30.99,1:57:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a separate personal self
Dialogue: 0,1:57:32.99,1:57:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,with a small s
Dialogue: 0,1:57:35.12,1:57:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,that is separate from the infinite oneness.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:37.12,1:57:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If you constantly
Dialogue: 0,1:57:41.64,1:57:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,identify with the field
Dialogue: 0,1:57:43.77,1:57:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,you will catch, the witness observer
Dialogue: 0,1:57:45.77,1:57:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,will see that everything is happening
Dialogue: 0,1:57:47.77,1:57:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,spontaneously.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:50.12,1:57:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We saw it happen spontaneously this morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:52.12,1:57:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where things say
Dialogue: 0,1:57:54.12,1:57:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,things happen spontaneously
Dialogue: 0,1:57:56.12,1:57:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,as a result of intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:58.12,1:58:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Audit came out of the audience, didn't it?
